# Use below link to install official steps to install aws cli on your system

https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/getting-started-install.html

# for Linux system 

Steps:- Download the installation file

curl "https://awscli.amazonaws.com/awscli-exe-linux-x86_64.zip" -o "awscliv2.zip"
unzip awscliv2.zip
sudo ./aws/install
 
